From d0d37b91d90acedfb1bb406e535463b9751527fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kol Crooks <kol.crooks@datadoghq.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 16:52:14 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Phase E: delete unused KrtPrMultiDiff + dead diff CSS

Phase D replaced KrtPrMultiDiff with KrtPrFlatDiff (one DiffEditorWidget
per file, content-sized). The old MultiDiffEditorWidget-based renderer
and its associated CSS rules are no longer reachable from any code path,
so wipe them.

Deletions:
- krtPrMultiDiff.ts (entire file, 292 lines)
- ~285 lines of CSS for the old per-section/per-line/zone-host/composer
  styling that the flat-diff cards don't use
- Stale comment refs to KrtPrMultiDiff in krtPrFlatDiff.ts and
  krtPrCommentController.ts

No behavioral change.
